MSNBC, and personally, I think it is a bad mistake to let her walk out the =
door,=E2=80=9D Maddow said, later adding that it was =E2=80=9Cunnerving to =
see that on a network where we=E2=80=99ve got two=E2=80=94count =E2=80=99em=
, two=E2=80=94nonwhite hosts in
